## Step 4 — Update STEM_CONFIG consumer (UI components)

The UI currently renders one fader per entry in STEM_CONFIG. Switch it to render from `currentSong.stems` instead. This is a small change in whichever component maps STEM_CONFIG to fader rows — find it with grep and do a surgical edit.

