## Step 5 — Build, verify, commit, deploy

1. `npm run build` in demo-src — confirm no errors.
2. Copy `dist/*` to `public/demos/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/` in michaelwegter.com.
3. Load the demo locally — confirm stems load (network tab), playback starts, faders work for all stems of all 3 songs.
4. Commit all changes in michaelwegter.com (audio assets + rebuilt bundle).
5. Push to main — GH Pages auto-deploys.

No media capture, no proposal writer re-run.

